# Upload auto-parse provider selection.
#
# Do NOT pin this to "none" here: a value in this committed file lands in
# process.env and OVERRIDES the auto-detect in src/lib/parse/extract.ts, which
# turns the extractor on whenever ANTHROPIC_API_KEY is set as a Vercel secret.
# Pinning it "none" silently disables upload autofill even after the key is
# added — uploads then fill in nothing. Leave it unset so auto-detect wins; set
# PARSE_PROVIDER=none in the Vercel dashboard only if you want to force it off.
